  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/9eda2c2b7008a9519e2c82726e5ae2f4.poster.avif?t=1769680835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/9eda2c2b7008a9519e2c82726e5ae2f4.webm?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/9eda2c2b7008a9519e2c82726e5ae2f4.mp4?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME TO FOOTBALL STREAKER SIMULATOR</h2><br>You won't find boring player formations, greedy licensed football players, gameplay that remains unchanged for years, or a pile of loot boxes with cards.<br>Just pure football fun.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JUMP INTO THE FOOTBALL FIELD</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/121c42e472b3f4f28342cccc8649c6e4.poster.avif?t=1769680835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/121c42e472b3f4f28342cccc8649c6e4.webm?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/121c42e472b3f4f28342cccc8649c6e4.mp4?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REALISTIC SIMULATION OF SIMULATIONS</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/8c150c14bc74817ad6284438ed2d309d.poster.avif?t=1769680835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/8c150c14bc74817ad6284438ed2d309d.webm?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/8c150c14bc74817ad6284438ed2d309d.mp4?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RUIN THE GAME FOR EVERYBODY, INCLUDING YOURSELF.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/c0055b451bf4372e43815fe0008f5ca7.poster.avif?t=1769680835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/c0055b451bf4372e43815fe0008f5ca7.webm?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/c0055b451bf4372e43815fe0008f5ca7.mp4?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RUN IN DIFFERENT HATS!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/cd995b4c9f7d39f115f8e05236553f7f.poster.avif?t=1769680835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/cd995b4c9f7d39f115f8e05236553f7f.webm?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/cd995b4c9f7d39f115f8e05236553f7f.mp4?t=1769680835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SCORE GOALS!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234470/extras/86c8a3860832cb7046ee16a2bbe76484.poster.avif?t=1769680835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste